{"tid":1253262,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】#LovePaMaChallenge #我反送中 #我愛爸媽","createTime":"2019-06-23T12:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T11:44:36.000Z","uid":66909,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5de8fbcff842f7711f8961b740e5b874423699","tid":1253262,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"見時事台好多post 傾緊條世代分化片<br />\n大家覺得有冇可能用social media 整個 #LovePaMaChallenge 以正視聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡單步驟：<br />\n1. 用social media 出一張自拍，可出樣可遮樣，出樣者自己衡量privacy setting ，平台最好用Facebook <br />\n<br />\n2. 手舉住一個紙摺心心，再加一張紙寫住「我反送中」+「我愛爸媽」<br />\n<br />\n3. Hashtag #LovePaMaChallenge #我反送中 #我愛爸媽<br />\n<br />\n條橋係極度老土兼肉麻，但有時就係温情嘢先最work<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過連登力量推出去，只要參與人數夠多，推上baby kingdom 推上新假期，就一舉反cap <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 温情牌正氣易入屋，唔理咩階層派系都受，夠多人做就有news angle<br />\n<br />\n2. 雖然對家拍晒片，但佢只有一個人，69、612大家應該已經知道人海戰術我哋冇得輸，只要人數夠多，足以證明拍片者只係個別極少數聲音，並不代表年輕人意見<br />\n<br />\n3. 當眾表明心跡，向港共表示我哋香港人團結一心，分化不攻自破，唔使旨意再喺G20前搞小動作打輿論戰<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4760959247a3f4a5da68963f93119a17014aa9","tid":1253262,"uid":66909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:09:30.000Z","msg":"膠橋自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0229dfd38ac637e1186f8134770c1ecfd00e74","tid":1253262,"uid":91519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"好似OK, 幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dd956a139c96f30de85678908f7b2257ca3a467","tid":1253262,"uid":66909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T13:57:33.000Z","msg":"其實件事就好似集體玩電話燈一樣膠<br />\n但庸俗社會正正就係有呢方面嘅需求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922d2205ec4f5507e6f1ec1c680d2dcdf55ac677","tid":1253262,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"對付謠言最有效嘅方法就係企出嚟闢謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對家揾一個人屈你一代人，我哋就一代人企出嚟指證佢唔係事實"},{"pid":"b8f69d60b566563a9b84443c473e1341b150d0a1","tid":1253262,"uid":190550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"對於擁有藍絲父母既我黎講<br />\n呢招雖然老土<br />\n但一定氹到佢地好開心<br />\n一條片點都比唔上自己仔女"},{"pid":"9b9f0ef65e50df99e7988511b21ed0fdb7dfa48f","tid":1253262,"uid":36114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T00:56:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"792338c7343937f973d0f38308294288624c4c3e","tid":1253262,"uid":265872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T03:47:59.000Z","msg":"推!<br />\n轉頭像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 低成本易spread"},{"pid":"4b3ce356fb58f2be747d0acee670f29813d4828b","tid":1253262,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"狗到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[文宣戰］開始發展到唔止攻年老人士<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254048</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f6aa02f75e17b7859782b14ff9f92f9c985d001e","tid":1253262,"uid":66909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f69d60b566563a9b84443c473e1341b150d0a1","tid":1253262,"uid":190550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T18:42:24.000Z","msg":"對於擁有藍絲父母既我黎講<br />\n呢招雖然老土<br />\n但一定氹到佢地好開心<br />\n一條片點都比唔上自己仔女"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T05:16:16.000Z","msg":"而且呢個方法比較一勞永逸<br />\n唔使每次對家出新片新圖我哋又再諗點拆<br />\n亦唔會將